{"tid":1022813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁國雄議員支持家庭團聚","createTime":"2019-02-15T09:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T10:57:26.000Z","uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b50039e0545d267192bdcd3c4edbf3f26d2a073f","tid":1022813,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T09:36:33.000Z","msg":"010016-011321 主 席<br />\n梁國雄議員<br />\n李卓人議員<br />\n政府當局<br />\n梁國雄議員表示 ⎯⎯<br />\n(a) 能否調整單程證制度，較多屬於<br />\n政治上的考慮，而非行政上的<br />\n關注；<br />\n(b) 內地當局對由內地來港的人口<br />\n流動施加管制，但香港方面卻<br />\n沒有相應的管制，並不公平；及<br />\n<strong>(c) 應充分利用每天 150個的單程證<br />\n配額，以促成家庭團聚。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr14-15/chinese/hc/sub_com/hs51/minutes/hs5120151123.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr14-15%2Fchinese%2Fhc%2Fsub_com%2Fhs51%2Fminutes%2Fhs5120151123.pdf&d=rje4l1xmTn6y9o%2BHBfPaf0PclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=d1246b63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr14-15/chinese/hc/sub_com/hs51/minutes/hs5120151123.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\npage5"},{"pid":"9f59934cdddf51a4353c09c11f16c63e73e878f5","tid":1022813,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T10:55:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0b957ffd46a7c6692e9adc6d813e1519bb17e4","tid":1022813,"uid":20725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T10:57:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}